Column.Name: Description
Column.Display: UNSAccountB was imported by Sync from Delinea Secret Server. ObjectGUID must be set to iserId from Delinea.
Column.Value: UNSAccountB was imported by Sync from Delinea Secret Server. ObjectGUID must be set to iserId from Delinea.

Column.Name: PreCode
Column.Display:
'Get AADUser account with same CN and Account Definition = configured value and ObjectGUID is not null 'It means that ADSAccount account was created in AD and it was imported into Delinea and then it was imported into UNSAccountB Dim accDefName = Connection.GetConfigParm("Custom\SecretServer\RegularAccountDefinitionName") Dim uidAccountDef = Connection.GetSingleProperty("TSBAccountDef", "UID_TSBAccountDef", "Ident_TSBAccountDef = '" + accDefName + "'").String Dim uidPerson = Connection.GetSingleProperty("AADUser", "UID_Person", "UserPrincipalName = '" + $cn$ + "' AND UID_TSBAccountDef = '" + uidAccountDef + "' AND Id is not null")
values("uidPerson") = uidPerson
Column.Value:
'Get AADUser account with same CN and Account Definition = configured value and ObjectGUID is not null 'It means that ADSAccount account was created in AD and it was imported into Delinea and then it was imported into UNSAccountB Dim accDefName = Connection.GetConfigParm("Custom\SecretServer\RegularAccountDefinitionName") Dim uidAccountDef = Connection.GetSingleProperty("TSBAccountDef", "UID_TSBAccountDef", "Ident_TSBAccountDef = '" + accDefName + "'").String Dim uidPerson = Connection.GetSingleProperty("AADUser", "UID_Person", "UserPrincipalName = '" + $cn$ + "' AND UID_TSBAccountDef = '" + uidAccountDef + "' AND Id is not null")
values("uidPerson") = uidPerson
